{"tid":1469640,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不割𥱊  但不是不檢討","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:28:00.000Z","uid":29760,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16611c069d840a06699dbfda43845d595dcc5f46","tid":1469640,"uid":29760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:31:48.000Z","msg":"首先要講明<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不分化不篤灰不譴責不互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大家都冷靜落嚟賽後檢討<br />\n不割𥱊唔代錯嘅決定繼續錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似塞鐵咁<br />\n8月5果次檢討完大部分人都覺得短期內唔好再做<br />\n平心靜氣  以事論事  不互屌<br />\n咁先係冇大台  社運2.0嘅典範<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山  唔係各自為政</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">要贏就要集合200萬人嘅智慧同經驗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612 721 811</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd09c75761969cb68347d9bf3680c8b385a08017","tid":1469640,"uid":95487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf591941a6ade35cdb86c9a8c5487fdd5ebf6b4","tid":1469640,"uid":29760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e70f79ab2dd82ef76fe444f32c3d9124945724","tid":1469640,"uid":29760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:33:34.000Z","msg":"612 721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56cc2801fa52425272cfc879aabc45aabcf9b5e","tid":1469640,"uid":29760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:36:48.000Z","msg":"612 721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dfe6bbb75a695341d5a6c5d9bdd5fc0088d6d9","tid":1469640,"uid":141135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"P牌正皮唔到 兄弟爬山係要一齊到山頂 唔係見兄弟行斜左淨係講不割咁就算 賽後檢討先能夠一齊上山頂"},{"pid":"1b83edb899b831e9d7994aa2b37b54ef7be37259","tid":1469640,"uid":29760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4dfe6bbb75a695341d5a6c5d9bdd5fc0088d6d9","tid":1469640,"uid":141135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"P牌正皮唔到 兄弟爬山係要一齊到山頂 唔係見兄弟行斜左淨係講不割咁就算 賽後檢討先能夠一齊上山頂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"同意  兄弟爬山係互雙幫助一齊爬<br />\n各自為政只係一盤散沙<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71842a86f38afe4bba229ffa2d97ed4d4f3a0958","tid":1469640,"uid":29760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"612 721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49db61943b0704b00a97f2eeb1a81f5df4607880","tid":1469640,"uid":29760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"612 721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fe578b82dbbe418e2375ee786c4d6e892cdb45","tid":1469640,"uid":141135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"818全民上街 五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}